{
  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, enhancing this framework can be achieved by incorporating emotion and sentiment labelling using established dictionaries.",
    "This additional layer of analysis can provide deeper insights into the context and tone of the text being analysed.",
    "Finally, expanding the size of the datasets used for training these models can significantly improve their performance and accuracy.",
    "By exposing them to larger and more diverse datasets, these models can better generalize patterns and nuances present in real-world data.",
    "ARTICLE HUMANITIES AND SOCIAL SCIENCES COMMUNICATIONS | (2024) 11:497 | https://doi.org/10.1057/s41599-024-02908-7"
  ]
}